TreePackage

Interface HuffmanTreeInterface<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryTreeInterface<SymbolFrequencyPacket<T>>, TreeInterface<SymbolFrequencyPacket<T>>, TreeIteratorInterface<SymbolFrequencyPacket<T>>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HuffmanTree

    public interface HuffmanTreeInterface<T>
extends BinaryTreeInterface<SymbolFrequencyPacket<T>>
    Operations are provided to interact with a Huffman encoding tree. This is similar to the DecisionTreeInterface from Chapter 23 of Data Structures and Abstractions with Java 4/e by Carrano
